OL,3,CMarcus Rashford joins Aston Villa on
OL,4,Cloan from Manchester United
OL,6,FMarcus Rashford has joined Aston Villa
OL,7,Fon loan from Manchester United for the
OL,8,Fremainder of the season.
OL,10,FThe 27-year-old forward had also been
OL,11,Flinked with moves to AC Milan and
OL,12,FBarcelona this month after falling out
OL,13,Fof favour at his boyhood club.
OL,15,FRashford, who joined United at the age
OL,16,Fof seven, has scored 138 goals in 426
OL,17,Fappearances since breaking into the
OL,18,Ffirst team in 2016 but has not played
OL,19,Fsince 12 December.
